data.description: This home is cozy yet spacious ! Centrally located in the heart of Lehigh Acres, this lovely home features three bedrooms, a bonus room and the home is tiled throughout. The exterior is complimented with a large shaded carport and a huge yard so your landscaping ideas can be infinite. Stainless steel kitchen appliances double sinks and a beautiful backsplash along with the spacious granite countertops makes preparing meals a breeze !  Don't delay, make this home yours today!
